{"tid":1953983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨：義務律師團隊將支援所有被Cap599無理檢控個案同黃店","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T00:02:16.000Z","uid":125168,"like":185,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffc59a0f526be531d6262ec0dc665bb0402fec5","tid":1953983,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3yPLPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3yPLPo.jpg&h=8a25a971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【抗疫為名 打壓為實】<br />\n政府因為武漢肺炎，引用Cap599章《預防及控制疾病條例》禁止聚集、限制餐廳。原意係好，但呢個政府永遠有權用盡！<br />\n<br />\n借抗疫之名，打壓831悼念者。明明林鄭話條例係要香港人「自律」，但成班警察「拎住雞毛當令箭」老屈幾個唔識嘅人「4人聚集」，又濫出告票，又推人埋牆搜身，搶巿民口罩「取證」，更加唔好講之前不斷借故騷擾「黃店」，多次入內騷擾客人！<br />\n<br />\n公民黨律師團隊將會義務支援所有被Cap599無理檢控個案同黃店，有需要嘅朋友請填寫網上表格，我地會有專人聯絡你。<br />\n<br />\n《599條例》無理檢控個案支援<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/CPCAP599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FCPCAP599&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=1c14f6a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/CPCAP599</a><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n圖片：立場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2939875456074917&amp;id=858421787553638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2939875456074917%26id%3D858421787553638&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=572ade5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2939875456074917&amp;id=858421787553638</a>"},{"pid":"0ad5e86be169c4941fc7c9710122144c5dcba821","tid":1953983,"uid":125168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"幫推告急！保住黃店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVBE73u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVBE73u.jpg&h=17a51ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDoXagQ.jpg\" d